### Kategori oluştur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Elektronik",
  "description": "Elektronik ürünler"
}

### Ürün oluştur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15",
  "description": "Apple iPhone 15 128GB",
  "price": 45000,
  "stock": 50,
  "categoryId": 1
}